hen Eigenheiten in der LXX hin zu beleuchten. So wird herausgearbeitet, wie die Themenfelder »Gott«, »Das Gesetz Gottes«, »Kult«, »Prophetie«, »Der Mensch«, »Weisheit«, »Volk und Bund« sowie »Verheißung« in den verschiedenen Teilen des Alten Testaments, Pentateuch, Propheten, Weisheitsliteratur, Geschichtsbücher und Psalmen von den Autoren der LXX verstanden und entsprechend übersetzt wurden.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Mai 2023) 7aRELIGION / Biblical Studies / Old Testament.2bisacsh1 aAusloos, Hans, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aAusloos, Hans, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aBrucker, Ralph, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCook, Johann, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDafni, Evangelia G., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEberhart, Christian A., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGzella, Holger, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHimbaza, Innocent, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLemmelijn, Bénédicte, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLemmelijn, Bénédicte, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aLoiseau, Anne-Françoise, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMeiser, Martin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPerkins, Larry, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPiquer Otero, Andrés, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRooy, Herrie van, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSalvesen, Alison, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators